title: Bagel & OJ Bundle Order ships & arrives separately from meals. | A breakfast classic
description: Has there ever been a more classic pairing than bagels & orange juice? This convenient bundle arrives at your door* with items individually packaged for your convenience. Have a delicious Lender's bagel (or two) at home, or throw a packet in your bag on your way to the office. We've paired our dozen plain bagels with Tropicana 100% Orange Juice and classic, single-serve Philadelphia Cream Cheese, but don't be afraid to get adventurous with your toppings! We love cucumber slices and fresh dill on our toasted bagels & cream cheese; the options are endless! *Your order will ship separately from your HF meals and may not arrive on your scheduled weekly delivery date (shipping is included in the total price). Customization of bundles is not available at this time.
